ket with spatula and set both aside."},{"content":"Blend yams <b>5 sec\/speed 8<b>. Add reserved steamed rice. <b>Insert butterfly whisk<b> and without measuring cup whip <b>40 sec\/\/speed 1.5<b>, while adding 2 oz butter, reserved grated Parmesan cheese, mascarpone and reserved steamed kale through hole in mixing bowl lid. Adjust seasoning to taste."},{"content":"Divide Yam Porridge into four bowls, sprinkle with reserved Brown Butter Sage Crumble and serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To view Chef Tim Hollingsworth prepare this dish: https:\/\/vimeo.com\/251745356"],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","40m","4 portions"]}